ves at school only to find that Haruhi is missing. Not only that, but Mikuru claims she has never known Kyon before, Koizumi is also missing, and Yuki has become the sole member of the literature club. The SOS Brigade seems to have never existed, nor has Haruhi Suzumiya. No one in the school has ever heard about her… except for Kyon.', 20.63, 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/original//x52WmUnfpB2AB0YUNGWJZaRzcBx.jpg', '2010-02-05', 'rcUiS0dpTkg', 7.9, 255, 4),
(65, 0, 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/original//gmECX1DvFgdUPjtio2zaL8BPYPu.jpg', '[]', '[16,10759,10765]', 95479, 'tv', 'Jujutsu Kaisen', 'ja', '呪術廻戦', 'Yuji Itadori is a boy with tremendous physical strength, though he lives a completely ordinary high school life. One day, to save a classmate who has been attacked by curses, he eats the finger of Ryomen Sukuna, taking the curse into his own soul. From then on, he shares one body with Ryomen Sukuna. Guided by the most powerful of sorcerers, Satoru Gojo, Itadori is admitted to Tokyo Jujutsu High School, an organization that fights the curses... and thus begins the heroic tale of a boy who became a curse to exorcise a curse, a life from which he could never turn back.', 424.96, 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/original//fHpKWq9ayzSk8nSwqRuaAUemRKh.jpg', '2020-10-03', 'VpO6APNqY1c', 8.6, 3603, 4),
